      <title>由于央行调查信贷风险，意大利 BFF 股价暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-10/bff-bank-shares-slump-32-amid-bank-of-italy-probe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[BFF Bank SpA 被监管机构勒令停止支付并审查其治理，导致这家意大利专业银行的股价跌幅创历史新高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-10/bff-bank-shares-slump-32-amid-bank-of-italy-probe</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 07:38:03 GMT</pubDate>
